                The Deputy-Chairman (Colonel Clifton Brown)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ef94f691-b581-4dcd-aac9-b24da5158b3f" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
