            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-39f14710-adf5-41e5-9685-8e4ed1de49e0">
                Mr. K. Griffith
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-39f14710-adf5-41e5-9685-8e4ed1de49e0" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
