<p class="">Obviously, there will have to be proper guarantees — disarmament, possibly the evacuation of places under discussion, and other obvious guarantees which must jump to the minds of hon. Members.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
