            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-0308a6d4-3281-4acd-abcf-55e6e1170072">
                The Under-Secretary of State for Foreign Affairs (Mr. Butler)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0308a6d4-3281-4acd-abcf-55e6e1170072" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
