<p class="">The hon. Member for Middlesbrough (Mr. K. Griffith) paid a great honour to our party when he said the Prime Minister showed as good patriotism as ever came out of Burke.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-0308a6d4-3281-4acd-abcf-55e6e1170072" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
