<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-487cb9e1-c3d5-49ac-874c-eb3a43c7da8c'>
            
<p class="">reasons why there has been delay in these negotiations. We are, therefore, in agreement with him on this point, and I trust that now, with what we have achieved over the last few months, with the growing strength of this country, with the determination we have shown, and with the success of our diplomatic efforts, we can at any rate face the summer ready for anything.</p>
